---
import HarnessOrbit from '../svg/HarnessOrbit.astro';
---
<section class="py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_380px] gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <!-- Pull quote -->
        <blockquote
          data-animate
          class="border-l-[3px] border-amber pl-8 mb-12"
        >
          <p class="font-display text-[clamp(1.5rem,3.5vw,2.5rem)] leading-[1.2] text-text">
            Stagent is the harness layer.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <div data-animate-stagger class="space-y-6 max-w-xl">
          <p data-animate class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Every product analyzed excels at its layer but leaves a gap at the
            layer above. Gateway patterns work but remain reactive. Parallel
            orchestration works but stays session-scoped. Multi-model routing
            works but is cloud-only and opaque.
          </p>
          <p data-animate class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Stagent is the system that consumes infrastructure, adopts
            application patterns, orchestrates across them, and adds the
            capabilities no existing product provides.
          </p>
          <p data-animate class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            Goal decomposition. Long-horizon persistence. Memory-native
            architecture. Graduated autonomy. Observable multi-agent execution.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Orbit diagram -->
      <div data-animate class="hidden lg:block" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
        <HarnessOrbit class="w-full text-text" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
